We have the option to run RuboCop on

* Whole project
* Files inside single folder
* Only on single file

Whole Project
    $ rubocop

Files inside single folder
    $ rubocop app

Single file
    $ rubocop app/models/user.rb

We can run auto correction with the following command:
    $ rubocop -a
    # or
    $ rubocop --auto-correct
    # or
    $ rubocop -A
    # or
    $ rubocop --auto-correct-all
